Comment.val: /*Service for the retreval of calculation components for the given transaction range. Only booked transactions will be returned.*/

Text.val: Range order is DESC so the startRecord indicates the last transaction number of the range:

SQL_STMT_U.val: select ai.trai_tr_re_id,ai.trai_tr_volgnummer,t.tr_transnummer,t.tr_rel1_rek2_munts,t.tr_trans_munts,t.tr_transdatum,t.tr_boekdatum,t.tr_valdatum,t.tr_settlementdatum from transactions t inner join tap_tr_rel_account_info ai on ai.trai_tr_volgnummer=t.tr_volgnummer inner join rekeningen r on r.re_id=ai.trai_tr_re_id inner join rekeningen_per_product rp on rp.rpp_productnummer=~1 and rp.rpp_volgnr_per_product=~2 and rp.rpp_relatienummer=r.re_nummer and rp.rpp_rekening_nummer=r.re_rekening and rp.rpp_rekeningsoort=r.re_soort and rp.rpp_valuta=r.re_muntsoort where ai.trai_tr_cl_id=~9 and ((~4=0 AND t.tr_transnummer >= ~3) or (~4<>0 AND t.tr_transnummer between ~3 and ~4) ) and ((~5='00000000' and ~6='00000000') OR (~5<>'00000000' and ~6<>'00000000' and t.tr_transdatum between ~5 and ~6) OR (~5<>'00000000' and ~6='00000000' and t.tr_transdatum >= ~5) OR (~5='00000000' and ~6<>'00000000' and t.tr_transdatum <= ~6) ) and (~7=0 or (~7=1 and t.tr_mut_gemaakt='J')) and exists(select 1 from trans_calc_components t inner join calculationrules c on c.cfcu_id=t.tcc_cfcu_id inner join deduction_definition d on d.id=c.cfcu_dedu_id where t.tcc_re_id=ai.trai_tr_re_id and t.tcc_tr_id=ai.trai_tr_volgnummer and (~8=' ' or d.definition_type=~8)) order by t.tr_transnummer DESC, ai.trai_tr_re_id ASC fetch first ~10 rows only

Text.val: v_NmbrOfTransactions is updated before the processing of the calc components hence compare with 'v_NumberOfRecords+1' :
tarifId (is only present in concepttransaction requests and not saved to the database, so will always be null)
calculationCurrency (is only present in concepttransaction requests and not saved to the database, so will always be null)
table (is only present in concepttransaction requests and not saved to the database, so will always be null)

ExpSyntax.val: IF(NOT ISNULL({0,1140850704}) OR NOT ISNULL({0,1140850705}) OR NOT ISNULL({0,1140850706}),'AMOUNT',IF(NOT ISNULL({0,1140850707}),'QUANTITY','NONE'))
